           manufacturer="Frans Englich"
           name="Modified Mamo">
           <db:para>Mamo from The Complete Guide to High-Fire Glazes, p. 121. Note that a mistake was done: there was 10 parts of Alumina in excess.</db:para>

           <recipe>
               <component idref="FeldsparFFF"       parts="25" replacementFor="CusterFeldspar"/>
